description: This Chainlink VRF top 5% score Parvati purrs with a rating of 70, and a multiplier of 3x. It has a total score of 210, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are 1 for North, Nine Lives for East, 3 for South, and 1 for West. Parvati has the personality suit of punter. A rendering of the card can be found at https://cards.ethercats.eth.link/40703-19312-3.html. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random NFTs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Parvati [210 Votes, Top 5% Score]
